  "label": "Tavin Arclight",
  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered, middle-aged human with brown eyes set beneath a heavy brow and a square, work-worn jaw. Black hair is kept in a short, practical cut, and the beard is maintained as close stubble that emphasizes a permanently coarse complexion. Taupe skin shows ingrained staining at the knuckles and along the forearms, the lasting marks of long service behind a bar. Their face carries the settled stillness of a career spent measuring patrons with a single glance and answering trouble with controlled economy.",
